sbol:Collection.dcterms:title: iGEM Parts Registry
sbol:Collection.dcterms:description: The iGEM Registry is a growing collection of genetic parts that can be mixed and matched to build synthetic biology devices and systems. As part of the synthetic biology community's efforts to make biology easier to engineer, it provides a source of genetic parts to iGEM teams and academic labs.

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K809331
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: GAL promoter + YFP + SPtom40 + Toc75+ ADH1 terminator
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: BioBricks of Toc75_SPtom40 (K809327) is linked with GAL promoter and ADH1 terminator. When expressed in cytoplasm, The Toc75 will be directed on mitochondrial outer membrane as a channel protein, and the YFP can function as a reporter.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Luohao Xu
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: All parts should be linked correctly without nonsense mutation and frameshift mutation

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: YFP_SPtom4
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: YFP is linked with signal peptide of Tom40, thus can be directed to mitochondrial outer membrane. It is used to test and signal peptide.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Luohao Xu
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: Both parts should be linked correctly without frame shift and nonsense mutation

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: Toc75
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Toc75 is the outer membrane translocation channel in chloroplast, which belongs to the transmembrane β-barrel protein family.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Luohao Xu
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: It is cloned by reversal transcription of Toc75 mRNA extracted from the cells of Cyanidioschyzon merolae

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: SPtom40
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This is the signal peptied of Tom40, which can direct the assembly of β-barrel protein into outer membrane of mitochondrion
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Luohao Xu
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Eukaryote-wide sequence analysis of mitochondrial β-barrel outer membrane proteins
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: No modification for the original sequence
